text: Blockade is a 1938 American war drama movie directed by William Dieterle and starring Henry Fonda, Madeleine Carroll, Leo Carrillo, Vladimir Sokoloff, Reginald Denny. It was nominated for 2 Academy Awards in 1939. ==Other websites== * * Category:1938 drama movies Category:1938 war movies Category:American war movies Category:1930s American drama movies Category:Movies directed by William Dieterle
